For thrown past the urn buttocks in addition to the fine is often sentenced to "link to the wipers": a week to clean the parks and beaches.
6 thousand rubles. pays the "criminal", who forgot to wash off the water in a public toilet, and when trying to relieve a small need in the elevator of a residential building, a special detector is triggered - doors are blocked and a signal is sent to the police.
