In general, there is a thought: no matter how hard you try, you will definitely break something.
It's not like that at all," Mohammed Kabir-Kajaria, the owner of a local travel agency, tries to dissuade me.
Especially fantastic laws exist only on paper, and in the last twenty years I have not seen anyone involved in their violation.
