Colin was not a public figure, although he was a former member of the AFL club's board of directors and, according to a 2015 biography of Eddie McGuire, the television star's best friend.
Fairfax Media contacted Colin and Paul and their lawyers on Friday.
Only Colin responded, with a text message stating that since the case had not yet been heard in court, "I really have nothing to say."
